{"tid":1756513,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"經濟日報消息: 中共對香港立場絕不軟化, 不會撤換中聯辦主任王志民","createTime":"2019-11-26T05:25:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-04T13:40:54.000Z","uid":134071,"like":81,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":102,"replies":[{"pid":"2b7465bbe6c5687f9804a4dc6e389aad0111364f","tid":1756513,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T05:25:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://china.hket.com/article/2506142/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchina.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2506142%2F&d=%2BSgL3cCD37R2%2BMUJ9ALV027D9zYHOB9IQ%2BPXuKXaEI4%3D&h=d780491e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://china.hket.com/article/2506142/</a><br />\n<br />\n路透社今天報道稱，香港中聯辦可能出現人事變動，<strong>涉及主任王志民。中方消息人士向本報表示，傳聞不確。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.etnet.com.hk/www/tc/news/home_categorized_news_detail.php?newsid=ETN291126511\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.etnet.com.hk%2Fwww%2Ftc%2Fnews%2Fhome_categorized_news_detail.php%3Fnewsid%3DETN291126511&d=%2BSgL3cCD37R2%2BMUJ9ALV027D9zYHOB9IQ%2BPXuKXaEI4%3D&h=4d6be2b9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.etnet.com.hk/www/tc/news/home_categorized_news_detail.php?newsid=ETN291126511</a><br />\n<br />\n至於北京會否調整策略？<strong>消息人士表示，中方當然會因應今次選舉做檢討，包括對未來立法<br />\n會和特首選舉的影響，但肯定不會因今次區選的結果而取態變軟。</strong>因為中方認為，今次反修例引發的風波，是一場維護與破壞一國兩制的鬥爭，也涉及外部勢力的介入。在北京眼中，泛民奪取區議會議席，只是第一步，下一步就是２０２０年立法會選舉，然後２０２１年選委會選舉，最後是２０２２年的特首選舉。<br />\n<br />\n  對於有傳北京或重新考慮特首林鄭月娥的去留，消息人士表示，國家主席習近平本月初刻意<br />\n高調在上海接見林鄭，表明中央對她高度信任，對其工作充分肯定；習近平此舉，就是要粉碎換人的傳言，中央的定調是經過深思熟慮，不可能在不足一個月內改變。<br />\n<br />\n  亦有人提及，一旦林鄭中途下台要補選，現時選委會區議會界別的１１７票，是否要改選換<br />\n人？答案是不用的，因為基本法附件一表明，選委會任期是５年。曾蔭權２００５年參加特首補選接替董建華時，也是由原本選出董建華的選委會選出。《<strong>香港經濟日報</strong>》（ｚｚ）"},{"pid":"71ed0536ed6dc729875d4745d5d0d19c98992118","tid":1756513,"uid":134071,"like":118,"dislike":0,"score":118,"citedBy":9,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T05:27:03.000Z","msg":"所以大家或者唔駛驚曾鈺成....<br />\n<br />\n曾鈺成既橋, 中共應該一條都唔會用...."},{"pid":"910dcfc4cce526e121f21ff7eb317baeae72f6e7","tid":1756513,"uid":49336,"like":40,"dislike":0,"score":40,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T05:28:01.000Z","msg":"重點 絕不軟化<br />\n<br />\n咪撚聽老油條曾鈺成口花花講嘢"},{"pid":"68aed9ceba8c92b19e22f48b57fb40dff94f9659","tid":1756513,"uid":218313,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T05:28:22.000Z","msg":"共狗:<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">要硬, 就死都要硬!<br />\n後果自負!</span></span>"},{"pid":"3b3ff0dfd11ddc1839e85de0449401e0be5fbd89","tid":1756513,"uid":188795,"like":38,"dislike":0,"score":38,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T05:28:51.000Z","msg":"當大家都諗到區選完左運動會下行既時候<br />\n完全忘記左中共最唔缺既就係火水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b8d48f833681f145d4011352a3ad8b425da5901","tid":1756513,"uid":279311,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T05:29:19.000Z","msg":"望都唔望佢換 就係因為咁嘅局勢先成就到香港人反抗嘅心<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4187bff53fc603ec1a85e872bb628b5dde177df7","tid":1756513,"uid":181789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T05:29:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c99fa641789e1f07c0a4c94dcde1f73cffdfb76d","tid":1756513,"uid":134071,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"3b3ff0dfd11ddc1839e85de0449401e0be5fbd89","tid":1756513,"uid":188795,"like":38,"dislike":0,"score":38,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T05:28:51.000Z","msg":"當大家都諗到區選完左運動會下行既時候<br />\n完全忘記左中共最唔缺既就係火水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T05:29:42.000Z","msg":"中共越撥火水, 美國介入既藉口就越多"},{"pid":"a30c4e312af2a877818d399d5defc8c9f4050a35","tid":1756513,"uid":33473,"like":55,"dislike":0,"score":55,"quote":{"pid":"71ed0536ed6dc729875d4745d5d0d19c98992118","tid":1756513,"uid":134071,"like":118,"dislike":0,"score":118,"citedBy":9,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T05:27:03.000Z","msg":"所以大家或者唔駛驚曾鈺成....<br />\n<br />\n曾鈺成既橋, 中共應該一條都唔會用...."},"citedBy":2,"replyTime"